item.title: [HELP] Running Client
item.dc:creator: @Skorge Skorge
item.description:
@Skorge wrote:

Search for keyword “Jframe” in your client and see how it is capitalized.
In example, if in your client, it is spelled “JFrame” rather than “Jframe”.
Edit keyword

Jframe

to

JFrame

The results may of course vary, I was just trying to explain that java is case sensitive, which is most likely the cause of the issue.
